title: 254: Predicting the Super Bowl Champion
itunes:title: 254: Predicting the Super Bowl Champion
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the Wild-Card round matchups before predicting the rest of the playoffs (4:50). DJ then reveals his Top 25 rookies this past season (28:26). The guys also pick who has the edge at each position in the College Football Playoff final between Georgia and Alabama (35:11).
